      "review_count": 15,
      "average_rating": 4.33,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">15 reviews for <span>Vyntech TWS</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-401\">\n<div id=\"comment-401\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Gautam agrawal</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>ANC is very usefull i can take my meetings peacefully</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-402\">\n<div id=\"comment-402\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">RAVIRAJ PATIL</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Very nice received product. Value for money. after two months I writing these review. Sound quality is awesome. ANC also good. I using these TWS under helmet on bike phone voice is good during call.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_3e31c2c5e3994dafae9a26d5f1ad43ca.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-403\">\n<div id=\"comment-403\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Hardik Pratik Patel</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>It's a fabulous product. Noise cancellation 5/5. Audio Quality and Codec 5/5. Design 5/5. Worth buying it. Value for money. Great Job Boat. Thank you Vyntech for the delivery.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-404\">\n<div id=\"comment-404\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Mayank paliwal</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Bass is less but trebel is good ... overall good TWS</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Mayank,<br><br>We have acknowledged your feedback regarding the bass levels. We will pass this suggestion to our audio tuning team to try working on it for future updates. In the meantime, you can customize your equalizer settings in the companion app.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-405\">\n<div id=\"comment-405\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Pragyan V.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Review after 1 month of usage.<br>It have different modes- normal, ambient, special and noice cancellation.<br>Good acitve noise cancellation, but it couldn't catch my voice clearly when I talk slowly.<br>Good battery but not as promised .<br>When i put it side it disconnect & don't reconnect automatically, we have to put it in the case back to get it connect again.<br>Sometimes it gives me headache with noice cancellation 😄<br>Overall a good product .</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Pragyan,<br><br>We apologize for the auto-reconnect glitch and ANC discomfort. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and a software support expert will help you update your firmware to fix the connectivity bugs and guide you on reducing the ANC intensity.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-406\">\n<div id=\"comment-406\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Pramisha</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Worth..</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-407\">\n<div id=\"comment-407\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sony Thomas</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Overall Good but not as Cmf buds 2</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_3855db5021d04d44a3bc20eba46771f7.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-408\">\n<div id=\"comment-408\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">A SWAROOP CHOWDARY</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Definitely for gaming but overall performance is ok it has battery life , easy to use, and it perfectly fits in your ear</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-409\">\n<div id=\"comment-409\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Shiristi rana</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>This is a grt product and i really like it.....the experience is really gud</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-410\">\n<div id=\"comment-410\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Akhil</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Good sound quality... And fit to ear.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-411\">\n<div id=\"comment-411\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Md Faizan Hussain</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Need to improve in bass of the buds and ANC is not better.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Faizan,<br><br>We apologize that the bass and ANC didn't meet your expectations. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our product expert can assist you in adjusting the equalizer settings for a punchier bass output and updating the ANC firmware.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-412\">\n<div id=\"comment-412\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Joseph j.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Good product for money</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-413\">\n<div id=\"comment-413\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Adarsh kashyap</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Sometimes it stucks but all other things are good</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Adarsh,<br><br>We apologize for the occasional stuttering. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our team will guide you through a quick software reset to ensure a seamless connection.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-414\">\n<div id=\"comment-414\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div